  "title": "A witness reports recurring sightings of a round yellow UFO in Sobradinho-DF [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/18/a-witness-reports-recurring-sightings-of-a-round-yellow-ufo-in-sobradinho-df-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-uR",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 10th, 1999</strong>. Time: 19h00. Duration: 1 hour. Three people observed a round yellow UFO flying slowly in Sobradinho, Distrito Federal. It was a clear sky night when the three witnesses spotted the UFO at great altitude moving towards Radial RDL 040 BRS [Brasília] in slow motion, almost stopping. The witness who reported the sighting to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command], also stated that she has &#8220;observed this object four times in the past 30 days.&#8221;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.542. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Sobradinho, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
